    citation: subpart-e-privacy-of-individually-identifiable-health-inform/164-502-uses-and-disclosures-of-protected-health-information
    span_id: HIPAA_removed/subpart-e-privacy-of-individually-identifiable-health-inform/164-502-uses-and-disclosures-of-protected-health-information/sent_0020
