  - If under applicable law an executor, administrator, or other person has authority
    to act on behalf of a deceased individual or of the individual's estate
  exceptions: []
  requirements:
  - The entity must treat an executor, administrator, or other person who has authority
    under applicable law to act on behalf of a deceased individual or the individual's
