    citation: subpart-e-privacy-of-individually-identifiable-health-inform/164-504-uses-and-disclosures-organizational-requirements
    span_id: HIPAA_removed/subpart-e-privacy-of-individually-identifiable-health-inform/164-504-uses-and-disclosures-organizational-requirements/sent_0010
